In the Vaadin view GSPs, you can use all of the 
[Grails tags|http://grails.org/doc/latest/guide/theWebLayer.html#tags] as you would in a
normal Grails GSP.

{note}
Sitemesh layout tags are currently not supported. Please use the Vaadin [layout|Tags] tag instead.
{note}

In addition, you can embed Vaadin components in GSPs using the tag library provided by this plugin:

{table}
 *Tag* | *Description*
 *LAYOUTS* |
 [accordion|Tags] | Adds a [Accordion|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/Accordion.html] component to the parent container.
 [horizontalLayout|Tags] | Adds a [HorizontalLayout|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/HorizontalLayout.html] component to the parent container.
 [include|Tags] | Includes the output of another controller/action in the current Gsp.
 [layout|Tags] | Renders the tag's body using another Gsp as a template.
 [location|Tags] | Adds the tag's body to the specified location in the parent container.
 [mainWindow|Tags] | Allows configuring the Vaadin application's main [Window|api:com.vaadin.ui.Window].
 [tab|Tags] | Configures a single tab of the parent [TabSheet|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/TabSheet.html] component.
 [tabs|Tags] | Adds a [TabSheet|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/TabSheet.html] component to the parent container.
 [verticalLayout|Tags] | Adds a [VerticalLayout|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/VerticalLayout.html] component to the parent container.
 |
 *TABLES* |
 [table|Tags] | Adds a [Table|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/Table.html] component to the parent container.
 [column|Tags] | Configures a single column of the parent [Table|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/Table.html] component.
 |
 *FORMS* |
 [form|Tags] | Adds a [Form|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/Form.html] component to the parent container.
 [field|Tags] | Adds a [Field|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/AbstractField.html] to the parent container.
 [checkBox|Tags] | Adds a [CheckBox|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/CheckBox.html] field to the parent container.
 [comboBox|Tags] | Adds a [ComboBox|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/ComboBox.html] field to the parent container.
 [currencySelect|Tags] | Adds a Currency-populated [Select|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/Select.html] field to the parent container.
 [customField|Tags] | Adds a [DefaultCustomField|api:org.grails.plugin.vaadin.ui.DefaultCustomField] to the parent container.
 [date|Tags] | Adds a [DateField|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/DateField.html] to the parent container.
 [file|Tags] | Adds a [DefaultUploadField|api:org.grails.plugin.vaadin.ui.DefaultUploadField] to the parent container.
 [listSelect|Tags] | Adds a [ListSelect|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/ListSelect.html] field to the parent container.
 [localeSelect|Tags] | Adds a Locale-populated [Select|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/Select.html] field to the parent container.
 [optionGroup|Tags] | Adds a [OptionGroup|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/OptionGroup.html] field to the parent container.
 [password|Tags] | Adds a [PasswordField|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/PasswordField.html] to the parent container.
 [select|Tags] | Adds a [Select|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/Select.html] field to the parent container.
 [text|Tags] | Adds a [TextField|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/TextField.html] field to the parent container.
 [textArea|Tags] | Adds a [TextArea|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/TextArea.html] field to the parent container.
 [timeZoneSelect|Tags] | Adds a TimeZone-populated [Select|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/Select.html] field to the parent container.
 |
 *MISC* |
 [label|Tags] | Adds a [Label|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/Label.html] component to the parent container.
 [link|Tags] | Adds a [GrailsButton|api:org.grails.plugin.vaadin.ui.GrailsButton] component to the parent container.
 [warning|Tags] | Shows a warning-type [Window.Notification|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/Window.Notification.html] in the application's main window.
 [error|Tags] | Shows an error-type [Window.Notification|http://vaadin.com/api/com/vaadin/ui/Window.Notification.html] in the application's main window.
{table}
